Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:08.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女孩是什麼顏色 男孩又是什麽顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:13.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女孩是紅色 男孩是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:20.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}某種顏色的女孩和某種顏色的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:25.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果邂逅 那在他們之間會產生什麼顏色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:28.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定 還是純白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如同新展開的畫布一般純潔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:33.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在未來才能決定顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:38.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那戀愛的顏色一定是白色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:45.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能將兩人的顏色染上的透徹的純粹的白色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:28.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}純白色的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:26.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 果然還是迷路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:30.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我又犯老毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在連自己在什麼地方都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 迷路還是好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃那麼漂亮 我一直都很擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:43.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用擔心的 迷路的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你迷路的話 只要我能找到就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:52.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 迷路的話只要讓哥哥找到就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:57.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 能照到那附近的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:59.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起來沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:32.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是是舊市街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:48.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:51.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}莫非那裡有各務賣場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:52.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:58.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:23.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:39.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 現在在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:44.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}離開剛才的地方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:50.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 被一隻奇怪的生物所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:54.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:58.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要再到處走了 會讓我找不著的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:03.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我知道了 我不再到處亂走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}（請給電池充電）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電池沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:15.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 附近有沒有什麼標誌物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:22.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都是圍墻 還有就是能看到山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:23.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:25.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結女的山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會馬上找到你的 等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:36.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我不會亂走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放心 我馬上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:34.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:40.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 你到底去了什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:53.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}金木樨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下雨了 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:38.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我答應哥哥不到處亂走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:51.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}您所撥打的電話不在服務區或已關機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:11.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 瓜生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生新吾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:22.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 是的 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:29.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 聯繫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:30.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你 是你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下雨沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:46.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事 愛理和我一起撐著傘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 是誰 剛才的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 愛理的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:52.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那這個手機是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 櫻乃 那你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:08:59.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:01.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:02.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}換我接電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}重新正式問候一下 我叫瓜生新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:12.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真對不起 我妹妹給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:19.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實我也迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:25.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}心裡也有些不安 反而是櫻乃幫了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:29.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 你要是道謝 我也會不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}兩個人都還迷著路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也是路痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才的 可不是值得笑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 從那裡能看到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡是上坡的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}遠遠可以看到街市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:56.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那條路的相反方向 是朝著山裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:02.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}朝著山一直向前走的話 應該可以到公園的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:06.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 哥哥現在在什麼地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:07.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也在舊市街
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:11.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在公園的西門附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:15.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 進公園以後的路 我也清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:31.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:36.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 再過一會就能見到哥哥了 再加油一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:40.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:43.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 連哥哥也這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過說得也是 一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:04.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是櫻乃的哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:11.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:13.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:19.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 真的萬分的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 反而是我得到了很多幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:27.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還想再見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:37.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是 因為 我們已經是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:53.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:02.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 熱水馬上就要燒好了 先進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:03.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差點就要得感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天開始就是十月了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:29.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也來洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我在裡面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事 我們是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可能沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:43.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被雨淋濕 身體冰涼的兄妹 在一起取暖...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爸爸和媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:16.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像接下來的一段時間會很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:26.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:27.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:32.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}各務賣場的魚店 有打折的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是昨天的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真正要買的是這個才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:39.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:45.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天是第一天 不能給哥哥隨便的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:14:02.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}琳琅滿目昂貴商品的各務賣場 和平常的我們完全無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:14.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 路痴的櫻乃冒著迷路的危險 到那裡去購物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}全都是為了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃冬天的校服 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:34.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}4個月沒見了吧 哥哥的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的就沒什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:41.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 櫻乃穿這衣服很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 準太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 是新吾啊 還有櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:54.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就讓我們出發去新學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}少女和她的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:05.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來我們就要踏上的路就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:11.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不錯呢 這樣可疑的舉止 我都燃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:18.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是被櫻乃給丟下了 新吾你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:27.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 聽說準太有婚約者了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 真尖銳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:32.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好的吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:54.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和女... 女生們的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:59.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得 好像有些要窒息一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那句話 我的立場怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:08.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們的母校 在新市街的各務台學園
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為陷入經營困境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在結姬女子學園的提議下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:15.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}進行了學校合併
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 說起舊市街的結女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:23.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結姬女子學園是歷史悠長的大小姐學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:29.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從十月份開始在那裡實驗性地 將一年級二年級選拔出來的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:32.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為試驗生就讀結女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:37.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯 我和櫻乃 還有準人都是其中的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:42.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}名門女校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:50.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:55.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:57.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼疑問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:09.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔從初次見面的人 得到我回來了的答覆還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:10.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:14.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}您一定很能幹吧 安潔莉娜大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:18.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}莫非您是華族或者貴族的後代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:21.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯 您的英姿依稀散髮出高貴的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:27.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能讓我心這樣砰砰直跳的 好久都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的是很紳士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔都陶醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結女的歡迎Neta吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:42.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得因太過吃驚而逃跑的人也會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:46.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個不用擔心 我會帶好路的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那你是 結女的女僕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:53.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是 教工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:57.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不不 雖然讓我來負責帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:59.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我安潔 是野生女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:01.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}野生?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女僕?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}野生女僕?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:12.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的名字是安潔莉娜·菜夏·史威爾 以後我們就認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:14.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:18.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們是暫時來上學的試驗生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:23.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在就帶你們去講堂 請移步這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:34.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過這真的是華麗的校舍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:38.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒想到還是野生女僕出沒的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:43.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過連野生女僕都遇到了 應該不會有更值得驚訝的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:06.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個生物 好像在哪裡見過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 椋梨 瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好厲害啊 大小姐學校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:26.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 這裡也像是能舉辦舞會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然出現女僕來迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:34.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}萬智老師 上去說幾句話比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:39.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}振作一點 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:42.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是… 年輕的男性有那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:44.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:45.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是結女的老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}集合場所在這裡就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:57.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 那個… 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}萬智老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:08.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學園長馬上就要來了 再稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:10.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:11.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好痛… 很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是一直都這麼強勢 會不受歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:22.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別囉嗦了 這樣會讓各務台的學生等很久的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:23.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:24.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我把學園長帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}八冢老師也振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:34.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 真的是太頑固了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:39.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道是生理中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼呀 因為宿醉讓他人久等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是母親提出的建議呢 學園合併
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:51.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎 我一直覺得是這樣的 你是很歡迎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才沒有歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:54.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然是愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:55.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 您們曾經謀面過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:05.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名 是結女的學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:11.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 又見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼 是愛理認識的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡是我們的學園
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論學園長是如何決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:34.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但決不是所有的學生都贊同合併的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:39.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至少我就 不歡迎你們男生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:43.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為這個結姬女子學園 是女校!

Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:54.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:30.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等 瓜生 你到底在看什麼地方呢
